{"tid":1664822,"cid":38,"subCid":0,"title":"[Respect] HKers help clean the mosque after police attack","createTime":"2019-10-20T10:09:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-23T09:51:59.000Z","uid":53666,"like":36,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"fa61177219dfeadb0eed8fcdcfaa9eed4e4b3db8","tid":1664822,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T10:09:21.000Z","msg":"Hong kong protesters gathered and cleaned the mosque that were attacked by HKPolice water cannon.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nThe largest mosque in Hong Kong - Kowloon Masjid and Islamic Centre - was a target of the latest water cannon splash during today's mass protest in Hong Kong against police violence and the anti-mask law.<br />\n<br />\nPolice used colored and pepper sprayed water cannon to shot at a peaceful crowed outside the mosque. A large part of the wall and gateway of the mosque were spammed with blue color.<br />\n<br />\nAn hour after the attack the police were gone and Hong Kong protesters gathered again to help clean the mosque with clean water and detergent to remove the blue marks left over by the water cannon splash.<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>暴狗剛才用水炮故意攻擊清真寺，現在有示威者幫忙清洗。警方此行為十分瘋狂，是公然侮辱伊斯蘭教，示威者對警方的行為予以最嚴厲的譴責！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iGXtB5R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiGXtB5R.jpg&h=2aadf87a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4iz0tcx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4iz0tcx.jpg&h=6d4c9fee&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sq75Ejd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsq75Ejd.jpg&h=7821d60d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n請廣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"cb5cfbd6ce7e4dcc314919f715de60ae45c71262","tid":1664822,"uid":303090,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T10:14:02.000Z","msg":"Look at what those protesters are doing after the rioters ruined the mosque wif their blue water"},{"pid":"52137fefc1762b52b1a6c6dc08f90e3194b1fffc","tid":1664822,"uid":53666,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T10:14:13.000Z","msg":"push.<br />\n<br />\nwas a sad scene but lovely HKers will not let that happen again!"},{"pid":"e88ca437dba05b9b02cb0e8b86fe54105148224b","tid":1664822,"uid":53666,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T10:15:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/EAh5ErH.jpg\" />"},{"pid":"4ec2ea44a63102972ffb5a01e10b07fde72bfbf2","tid":1664822,"uid":53666,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T10:16:09.000Z","msg":"terrible act by HK police<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/tfv3q7h.jpg\" />"},{"pid":"2877938dc833d63ccd83965da79af65137110465","tid":1664822,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T10:18:12.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4528e4f74218b730aab2db918172193222f9b8aa","tid":1664822,"uid":12517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T10:18:46.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"66607f3caffd897d210b9f4802a8ba4221f61425","tid":1664822,"uid":12517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T10:18:56.000Z","msg":"P"},{"pid":"72f121d3328ac4f47e0cc00d0261190903e2048c","tid":1664822,"uid":12517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T10:19:06.000Z","msg":"U"},{"pid":"96126baba918bea03efe22f4d4626553e7149851","tid":1664822,"uid":12517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T10:19:16.000Z","msg":"S"},{"pid":"350479a61eb47cb0b5ce0de1d6b2d7459d55ae35","tid":1664822,"uid":12517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl